SPOG has been a problem for some time.
https://nextdoor.com/p/-RFFpZKFCShw?post=3D471654107&ct=3DU-DqG8A-mlQG33iBp=
O9vEpWQ6i1EYN9KtcIkdz_ktKgSxAaakuoHqy3D7ycybjrq&ec=3DOWKiQRDj9vEHAYwTV6YMAR=
